  <members>
    <member name="T:System.ConsoleSpecialKey">
      <dduexml xmlns="http://ddue.schemas.microsoft.com/authoring/2003/5">
        <summary>
          <para>Specifies combinations of modifier and console keys that can interrupt the current process.</para>
        </summary>
        <remarks>
          <content>
            <para>The <codeEntityReference qualifyHint="true" autoUpgrade="true">P:System.ConsoleCancelEventArgs.SpecialKey</codeEntityReference> property returns the <codeEntityReference autoUpgrade="true">T:System.ConsoleSpecialKey</codeEntityReference> enumeration type.</para>
            <para>Simultaneously pressing certain key combinations signals the operating system to interrupt the currently running process. The two valid key combinations are <codeEntityReference qualifyHint="true" autoUpgrade="true">F:System.ConsoleModifiers.Control</codeEntityReference> plus BREAK (CTRL+BREAK) and <codeEntityReference qualifyHint="true" autoUpgrade="true">F:System.ConsoleModifiers.Control</codeEntityReference> plus <codeEntityReference qualifyHint="true" autoUpgrade="true">F:System.ConsoleKey.C</codeEntityReference> (CTRL+C).</para>
          </content>
        </remarks>
        <codeExamples>
          <codeExample>
            <legacy>
              <content>
                <para>The following code example displays the <codeEntityReference autoUpgrade="true">T:System.ConsoleSpecialKey</codeEntityReference> value that invokes the associated event handler.</para>
                <codeReference>console.cancelkeypress#1</codeReference>
              </content>
            </legacy>
          </codeExample>
        </codeExamples>
        <relatedTopics>
          <codeEntityReference autoUpgrade="true">T:System.ConsoleCancelEventArgs</codeEntityReference>
        </relatedTopics>
      </dduexml>
    </member>
    <member name="F:System.ConsoleSpecialKey.ControlBreak">
      <dduexml xmlns="http://ddue.schemas.microsoft.com/authoring/2003/5">
        <summary>
          <para>The <codeEntityReference qualifyHint="true" autoUpgrade="true">F:System.ConsoleModifiers.Control</codeEntityReference> modifier key plus the BREAK console key.</para>
        </summary>
      </dduexml>
    </member>
    <member name="F:System.ConsoleSpecialKey.ControlC">
      <dduexml xmlns="http://ddue.schemas.microsoft.com/authoring/2003/5">
        <summary>
          <para>The <codeEntityReference qualifyHint="true" autoUpgrade="true">F:System.ConsoleModifiers.Control</codeEntityReference> modifier key plus the <codeEntityReference qualifyHint="true" autoUpgrade="true">F:System.ConsoleKey.C</codeEntityReference> console key.</para>
        </summary>
      </dduexml>
    </member>
